&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;regolith-st&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;The st-term with some patches applied.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;regolith-styles&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Metadata that describes the UI look in Regolith.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

